In my life, i never know what I wanted to do. Is like that since my parents are asking me what I wanted to do when I become an adult.
And then, the covid 19 have arrived in our life. The hiatus at this epoque was verry important to me because i was able to think about what I wanted to do after in my life.
So, at this epoque we all kown that we have a lot of time to do the task that we have never do before because of the time. Personally, I had listened to music more than ever. And then I discover the kpop genre. I had lisented a lot of kpop music this then. I have fall in love to this music genre, and I wanted to me a part of it. So i ask myself how can I do to work in this industrie. The work that will suit me. And then I discovered the job of : artist manager ! So like that I can be with my idols and work in Paris ! I choose this job because I can't play an instrument and I can't sing, so the choice have reduced.
I do some reserch and I find some ecole of managment but It was verry expensive, and then I find the university of Rennes 2 and the departement of : information-communication, and I think it would suit well to do the job. So I had sucessed to arrive in this university and we will see if I will arrive to do what i want to be in the futur ! !
 This webpage performs keylogging of input typed into a texbox. In other words, when focused ont the textbox below, the page will record each time you hit a key or select text with your mouse. All of the data is stored locally on your machine in the DOM and is downloadable as a JSON file. More information about the motiation of this project and the forma of the procuded data are available here.
